</p></section><section id="M155104-B84" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph ">Answer</ph></title><table id="M155103-TB85" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="stage" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="20*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="20*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="60*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" namest="col1" nameend="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Classification 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Description 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Printing jobs</b> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> general</b> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Jobs are not printed anymore and media request not shown when quick move to tops.
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Greyed out jobs when printing job is cancelled and move to top. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Onyx</b>
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Print jobs individually is not converting job copies into layout copies (Onyx version 22.0.2)
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Controller</b> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Media calibration</b> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Canceled media calibration does not stop
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Media calibration takes 5 minutes longer than in the C1650
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Engine</b>
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">450002 PHD flash read/write error reduction of error occurence
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Error 450001 printheadCommunicationError reduction of error occurence
</p><p class="- topic/p "> "Replace" button for "Tissue cassette" is greyed out has been resolved. Replacement procedure for Tissue wiper has been implemented.
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Infinite error loop when tissue runs empty during top cover initialization
</p><p class="- topic/p ">White lines in white colour and inconsistent spit in standby leads to failing nozzles. Spit and prefire was implemented before PAINt step A and step B, the results will then be more reliable by detecting latent failing nozzles before maintenance decision to perform a purge/wipe. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Service</b> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Test prints</b> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">21-6-005 PQT white and flush prints are not working as specified is now solved.
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Installation</b> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> M-series installation via WebUI takes 2.5 hours. ISO file size has been drastically reduced due to a reduction of the print strategies, which makes the installation faster. 
</p></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></conbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-C96CD0FB-5FF2-4206-8F5D-73B1DC329368.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>R4.2.0.0</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
